{"tid":1746992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地指導球員性生活時間不要持續太長，最好女上男下","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T05:10:36.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46aa74edcab2921edb36bb69c8dac0d3c944ade2","tid":1746992,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"國際米蘭主教練干地又出奇語，他指導球員，在賽季期間，性生活的時間不要持續太長，而且最好採用女上男下的體位。<br />\n<br />\n  在接受法國《隊報》採訪時，干地道出了自己的理念，他認為，作為職業足球人，一切都是為了獲勝，任何犧牲都是必要的。「競爭在我看來就是戰鬥，是你死我活的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n  干地說，「我專注於這樣的理念，到最後只可能有一個人還站著（其他都倒下了），我會盡一切全力讓我的球隊成為那一個。」<br />\n<br />\n無微不至的干地<br />\n<br />\n  接下來，干地談到了為了達成勝利目標，在各方面都需要注意，甚至給出了在床上的具體指導：「在賽季過程中，性生活的時間不能持續太久，要盡可能的少用力，最好是讓伴侶在你的上面。」<br />\n<br />\n  看起來，干地為了獲勝，實在是操碎了心，只是不知道他這樣的「無微不至」，是否會讓球員們感到反感"},{"pid":"87166b45610e14a8e3dc26ec27c91f28f1a1fd00","tid":1746992,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5a3a60520957ca2caac78d3d2806f089a52c96","tid":1746992,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=859ca0ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e474dcb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/n</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，星期日7am 見)"},{"pid":"564320fe2fea60c70f8c28a1f1eb0a54efe6f13d","tid":1746992,"uid":135957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3ffea15159b1ba2e818d8849022583401b672e","tid":1746992,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:26:06.000Z","msg":"坐嘅姿勢唔好咪仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6bfdfce742cba4dca028f2a6b8c25e1dc2111c","tid":1746992,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"男上男下"},{"pid":"815bfbcff38e7687e377b75223a8783e567e8d73","tid":1746992,"uid":36724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"on 9咁不如唔好練波，出入搵人用輪椅推，乜都唔好用力"},{"pid":"eb43a44544f2b832b83e0de18e4ad0c1ce18ce27","tid":1746992,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"re